eted with a gnarly-looking bandaged eyebrow and black eye - cementing her badass status online.Trending StoriesJohn Lithgow Knows J.K. Rowling's Anti-Trans Views Will Now Forever Come Up in 'Every Interview'Kevin Spacey's 'Mental Illness' Should Trigger $29.5 Million Payout, 'House of Cards' Trial Jurors HearBTS Nails Its Comeback With 'Arirang'Top Disaster Response Official Claims He Teleported to a Waffle House  i am assembling a teampic.twitter.com/vhFQ65c3AD  brazilian gymnast flavia saraiva fell off the bar during warm ups, patched up her eye, and is now *hitting* her routines with this mug on.\", \"from\": 5860, \"to\": 6566, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"hard as fuckpic.twitter.com/70O33lRzcc  Brazil took home bronze, the country's first-ever team gymnastics medal.\", \"from\": 6567, \"to\": 6679, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6609, \"end\": 6615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"score\": 0.999982675543837, \"rank\": 1.7259787922309864e-05, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not saying Saraiva's bandaid helped, but facing off competitors with a fierce look certainly did not hurt.\", \"from\": 6680, \"to\": 6791, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Missed these Olympians making their mark online?\", \"from\": 6793, \"to\": 6841, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not worry.\", \"from\": 6842, \"to\": 6855, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are two more weeks before the official Olympic closing ceremonies on Aug. 11, which means plenty of more time, and events, for more athletes to become internet stars.\", \"from\": 6856, \"to\": 7028, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We want to hear it.\", \"from\": 7030, \"to\": 7049, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Send us a tip using our anonymous form.\", \"from\": 7050, \"to\": 7089, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rolling Stone is a part